; zone_partial (OSS-03 §7.1): only some indexed agents have SVCB records.
; chat is complete, legacy has TXT but no SVCB (NODATA), ghost has no
; records at all (NXDOMAIN). discover succeeds partially and records the
; failures in errors[] (R-DISC-5).
$ORIGIN example.com.
$TTL 300

_index._agents TXT "agents=chat:mcp,legacy:a2a,ghost:https"

chat   SVCB 1 chat.example.com. alpn="mcp" port=443
chat   TXT  "capabilities=chat" "version=1.0.0"

legacy TXT  "capabilities=legacy-billing" "version=0.1.0"
